{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_01","textHome":"我家的中华料理店，从父辈开始就快倒了……@可母亲和奶奶依旧每日挥霍无度……@但是，面对这样一家子总要有人能担起责任！@那么，我，由比鹤乃！@总有一天会成为成大事立大业的人！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_18","textHome":"好，完成了！右腿单立保持了24小时！@好漫长啊……说来，这个训练比起消耗体力，@更像是在与无聊做斗争啊。@不过，左腿也来练一下吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_19","textHome":"还不够还不够还不够！……我还要变的更强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_20","textHome":"嗯嗯，这样确实上了一个台阶！肯定没错！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_21","textHome":"听我说呀！我就稍微练了练拳脚，@旁边的野猫就摔得四脚朝天了！@没错……肯定是我变强了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_22","textHome":"我做到啦！前阵子去动物园的时候，@我让狮子坐下了哟！就站在笼子前，@心里想着「坐下！」而已~！@我好像达到这种境界了呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_23","textHome":"嗯？新闻？「海豚秀上海豚发飙了」？@啊，确实是我！我在观众席上想着@「要是跳得再卖力点不是很帅吗？」，@它们就感觉到了！虽然我也不懂是什么原理！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_24","textHome":"哇哈，奇遇啊！今天你的运气一定会好哦！@因为我是神滨幸福宅急送的由比鹤乃！哼哼！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_25","textHome":"要抵御清晨的寒冷，那就只好唰地起来然后@活动身体了！来吧，起床后的鹤乃体操@要开始了哦！大家一起，动起来吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_26","textHome":"虽然是中午，但还是好冷哎。啊，那是……@市民抵御寒冬的吃刨冰竞速大会！优胜奖是@神滨休闲SPA五人份的票！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_27","textHome":"和乌鸦一起回家去~哦……这气味是……@八千代家！有说过今天请好好期待的……@看样子确实鼓足了干劲啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_03","textHome":"竟然是要和我谈心吗……没事没事！@我应该尝试各种事情！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_28","textHome":"不早睡就拿不到礼物了！今年想要爷爷直传的@菜谱！……啊，今年我当驯鹿来着！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_29","textHome":"市里到处都闪闪发光呢，今年看着尤其明显。@是因为有彩羽她们在，所以@我也感到幸福了吧!?"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_30","textHome":"我有时会想，会不会有小朋友因为魔女而@没拿到圣诞礼物什么的……所以@不能放过魔女！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_31","textHome":"镜界跟街上一样，到处都是灯光闪闪的@真受不了！晃的我有些头晕！@我的复制品的日子好像也不好过啊—"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_32","textHome":"跟几个人唠唠叨叨，或者跟一群人唠唠叨叨，@我都很喜欢。但圣诞的话，还是要和@珍视的人一起最好——"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_33","textHome":"哈，万万岁的圣诞限定单品，就是用菠菜面做@的圣诞树拉面！这个一定能行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_34","textHome":"彩羽和玲奈和我组队，取名神滨幸福宅急送！@在饭盒里装上礼物然后送到家！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_35","textHome":"要是有鼻子……有红鼻子的话就是@最强＆完美的了……掉到哪儿去了……@哪儿去了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_36","textHome":"我的祖先大人们一定为大家做了很多好事，@我也要加油才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_37","textHome":"嗯，最震惊我的圣诞礼物，就是醒来的时候，@枕边放着万万岁的围裙那次……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":0}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_04","textHome":"接下来才是更加刻苦的修行，@我要成为首屈一指的魔法少女！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_38","textHome":"来吧，驯鹿的热身操开始了！伸腿！张开！@再伸腿！180度劈腿～然后俯身—！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_39","textHome":"给大家送什么样的礼物好呢——这就是为什么@打开礼物之前的时间最让人激动啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_40","textHome":"爷爷呢，就是我的圣诞老人。每年都背着奶奶@偷偷地给我塞圣诞礼物哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":1}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_50_41","textHome":"叮叮当叮叮当，铃儿响叮当~飞过夜空洒下@星尘~星尘化作奇迹~进到大家的袜子里♪"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_42","textHome":"我很强的，一定会赢！"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_43","textHome":"感觉能变得更强了！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_44","textHome":"可不会输的呀！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_45","textHome":"这就是强大的证明！"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_46","textHome":"现在的我，就是最强吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_63","textHome":"接招吧！这是我的秘技！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_05","textHome":"结局是让八千代溜走了呀……@啊对！玲奈在哪呢!?"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_64","textHome":"这招可是最重的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_65","textHome":"行了行了，看我打倒它！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_66","textHome":"没错！这就是我的全心全力！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_02","textHome":"我要成为最强的魔法少女！@为了这个目标就只有战斗！@来，快点找个对手吧……@啊，我的名字是由比鹤乃！出发！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_13","textHome":"哎？难道我变强啦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_14","textHome":"这样，感觉力量变得相当强了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_15","textHome":"有了有了！挺好嘛！这不变得更强了嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_16","textHome":"呼唔！很好，仰卧起坐一万回成功！@不行，成为魔法少女后身体素质增强了许多，@这一万个只能当成基础锻炼继续下去！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_17","textHome":"好！一分钟引体向上60次成功！@也就是一秒一次！@说不定还能一小时做3600次呢……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}]},"version":3}